The bad thing about Grovehill is the shops. There is glass all over the pavement because teenagers smash bottles. There are a lot of sweet papers around because children just throw them on the ground. The nice thing is that many friends live here. There are lots of exciting things to do, especially at the playing fields and the BMX track. Children also go to Brownies, Cubs, Ballet, Dancing and Karate.
